data.description: Once you enter, you won't want to leave! Welcome to this amazing 4 Br, warm and welcoming home! The bright, open concept floor plan lives well! Beautiful entryway with high ceiling, clerestory window and wood beams. Things to love: granite countertops thru-out, great room with fireplace, chef's kitchen boasts work island, industrial hood vent, farmhouse sink. Inviting primary bedroom with high ceilings appointed w/ wood beams, custom shelving, large walk-in closet. Luxurious primary bathroom w/ double sinks, rain shower head and extra large soaking tub.  Laundry Rm with wash basin. Lots of storage inside plus shelving in the garage. Easy attic access w/ retractable staircase. Covered patio leads to Immense backyard; ready for you to use your imagination, plus view of our beautiful mountains! SOLAR PANELS to be paid off by seller! As a clean energy source, it's great for our environment and saves on your electric bill. Recharge your senses here & enjoy this stunning Palo Verde resale! Verify schools & zoning.
